710113f-a.title: Manhattan: 8th Avenue - 22nd Street (West)
710113f-a.text:
Eighth Avenue, east side, north across W. 22nd Street.
Views 2 and 3 are photographed from a point slightly above same.
Note the absence of the street car tracks observed in the
earlier views. These were remoed by the C. W. A., subsequent
to subway construction underground.
June 25, 1928
February 13, 1932
May 10, 1939
P. L. Sperr
NO REPEODUCTIONS
